<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/0> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 0 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1. Introduction into Oral Communication. Role of speaker and listener. Listening for main ideas and for specific information. Listening and note-taking."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/1> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 1 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.1. Strategies for Oral Communication. Useful language. Oral Communication Workshop: signposting language Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/10> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 10 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.2. Oral presentation preparation and design (Rewilding projects in Europe). Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/11> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 11 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.3. Evaluation of Oral presentations: Criteria for evaluation. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/12> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 12 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6. Listening for specific information. Recording information in note-form. Vocabulary building"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/13> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 13 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6.1. Individual presentations on selected topics (Endangered species, wildlife management) Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/14> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 14 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "7. Group presentation practice (Ecoregions; Forest ecosystems). Selecting main and subsidiary points. Recording data in note-form. Pronunciation and stress. Vocabulary building"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/15> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 15 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "7.1. Listening skills (Doñana NP, Spanish National parks videos) Vocabulary building. Recording information: summarizing Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/16> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 16 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "7.2. Individual presentations on selected topics (Forest ecosystems) Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/17> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 17 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "8. Strategies for writing essays/papers. Reading academic articles. Ecological networks Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/18> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 18 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "9. Academic writing style. Citation. Plagiarism. Referencing sources. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/19> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 19 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "10. The term paper: genre constraints. Planning, outlining and drafting.Revising, editing & publishing Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/2> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 2 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2. Information transfer in pairs (Structure of a university degree). Listening and recording information in note-form in a flowchart. Vocabulary building."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/3> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 3 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.1. Group oral presentation practice (MSc Erasmus Mundus forestry degrees) Written versus spoken English. Selecting and ordering information. Presenting information from notes. Introduction to academic writing. The writing process. Academic world list Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/4> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 4 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.2. Listening skills (MSc University of Cumbria Video) Note-taking techniques. Outlining: selecting and structuring main ideas, supporting ideas and details. Reporting from outlines to text. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/5> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 5 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3. Pair presentation practice (IUCN Red list categories). Group presentation practice (IUCN Report on biodiversity in Spain)."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/6> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 6 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.1. Group information transfer (Endangered wildlife species). Jigsaw listening and recording information in note-form. Pronunciation and word stress. Paraphrasing and Summarizing (Endangered species, Species recovery) Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/7> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 7 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4. Describing a process. Language of cause-effect. Expressing causal relationships. Paragraph building, reference and cohesion (Loss of biodiversity) Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/8> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 8 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5. Listening to a live conference (Rewilding Europe conference). Recording information: from notes to outline."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/135004701/2025-26/syllabus/9> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 9 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.1. From listening to participating in a debate. Debate skills and language (Wilderness, Rewilding, Tourism) Sin subniveles"@es .

